description:
In this edition of Homozeit, Jack and Miles discuss Prince William's Jamaican royal tour, Barry Keoghan playing the Joker, iPhone launching digital state IDs and drivers licenses in Arizona, Californians getting up to $800 in gas tax rebates, North Korea's ICBM tests, and the USMNT run for the World Cup!
